reviews.text: If you like to eat, GO HERE. Hubby and I went on a date night to the East Market. We decided to walk around first and then decide.  This is the first place...
Aw man, this place is delicious!! I had the Just Loaded Fries and they were fantastic. I would make a trip back down there just for those. Who could turn...

I had every intention of getting something sensible for dinner and then saw loaded fries at Just Chicken and there went that plan.  

They start with fresh...
